        "text": "to give freely",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "” “largiri.” The word appears to be used designedly by St Mark, implying that Pilate, who from his character might have been expected to extort money from the wealthy “counsellor,” ",
